rows.label: bf10260100_0020
rows.name:
The Conduit, which fell into a stubborn silence after
the world's end, has begun stirring once more.

rows.label: bf10260100_0040
rows.name:
The power you and Pneuma exercise
is the Conduit's power.

rows.label: bf10260100_0050
rows.name: It comes leaking out of some far-flung dimension.

rows.label: bf10260100_0060
rows.name: And it is a power we can know nothing about.

rows.label: bf10260100_0080
rows.name: The world may be about to change.
